tourBios.otherCarHigh: Two-time Junior America's Cup winner...Three-time Oregon State champion. Was the 2006 Big 12 Conference Newcomer of the Year...Made Web.com Tour debut as an amateur at the 2004 Oregon Classic, where he missed the cut.
tourBios.personal: Instructor is Smiley Jones...Won the 2011 Brickyard on the NPGT...Follows Los Angeles Lakers...Favorite show is "Entourage" and top movies are "Remember the Titans" and "Love & Basketball."...Listens to the Dave Matthews Band and Weezy...Enjoys vacationing in Hawaii...Favorite gadget is his range finder...Carries peanut butter and jelly sandwiches and trail mix in his golf bag...Not many people know that he is self taught in golf...Bucket list includes going 200 mph in a car, skydiving and playing golf in Scotland.
